						               													<description>Conquer Mount Eldmont and return the gold to the dwarves! For two thousand years Mount Eldmont remained impregnable&amp;hellip; In its caves were stored tens of thousands of gold crystals, once stolen by an insidious Dragon. Gold rightfully belongs to the dwarf clans, and today they are ready to restore justice. Are you ready to join the battle for Eldmont? Then go ahead! Be the first in the battle for the treasures of Eldmont!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Your task is to collect as many gold crystals as possible in your chests. You have to play only for yourself, try to outwit your rivals &amp;mdash; after all, it is your clan that should own the gold!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It's very simple to do this &amp;mdash; lay out action cards and expose your dwarves. A certain combination of moves will give you gold crystals. Keep them in your chests so that your rivals don't guess how close you are to victory.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But don't forget, there is an insidious Dragon hiding in the depths of the caves. He has not yet noticed the arrival of guests in his domain and is sleeping sweetly on the golden mountain. But one wrong move, and you will fall into his clutches! Enlist the support of a Wizard, control the elements and beware of the monster.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The one who collects the most crystals is recognized as the winner of this game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
